MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

98-579. Planet Earth Entertainment, Inc. v. Ohio Liquor Control Comm.

Franklin App. No. 97APE06-744. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to dismiss on suggestion of mootness,

It is ordered by the court that the motion to dismiss on suggestion of mootness be, and hereby is, granted.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., dissent.
